# Cloudflare Pages headers (members' app — app.taimotion.com)
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/
# Security headers apply to every response. Caching is left to Cloudflare's
# defaults; asset cache-busting keeps relying on the ?v=NN query strings.
/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()
  # Members-only app — keep the entire subdomain (guides, PDFs, urls) out of search engines.
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow
